title: CMOH North 24 Parganas Jobs 2026 - Apply Online for 02 Specialist Posts
description: The Chief Medical Officer of Health, North 24 Parganas (CMOH North 24 Parganas) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 02 Specialist Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MBBS, DNB, PGDM, and Post-graduation can apply for the CMOH North 24 Parganas Jobs 2026. The interested applicants can apply in online mode.
